radfu (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add DLM state transit command
  * Add initialize command (factory reset)
  * Add boundary setting command
  * Add parameter setting command (one-way lockdown)
  * Add key management commands (KEY, KEY_VFY, UKEY, UKEY_VFY)
  * Add boot code detection delay for reliable connection
  * Complete implementation of all 20 RA4M2 bootloader commands

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Wed, 01 Jan 2025 16:00:00 +0100

radfu (0.0.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add macOS support
  * Add Linux ARM64 builds
  * Add install.sh script for easy installation
  * Use git describe for automatic versioning
  * Fix man page formatting

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Mon, 30 Dec 2024 22:00:00 +0000

radfu (0.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release

